    <h2>PENALTIES (Subtracted from Daily Score):</h2>
    <div class="scoring">
        <ul>
            <li>2+ days without laundry = <span class="penalty">-3 points</span></li>
            <li>No clean cutlery left = <span class="penalty">-5 points</span></li>
            <li>No clean towels available = <span class="penalty">-5 points</span></li>
            <li>Family complaint about mess = <span class="penalty">-2 points</span> per complaint</li>
            <li>Unplanned daytime napping = <span class="penalty">-1 point</span></li>
            <li>Skipped appointment = <span class="penalty">-3 points</span></li>
            <li>Avoided TAFE/responsibilities = <span class="penalty">-2 points</span> daily (escalates weekly)</li>
            <li>3+ days without Extras done = <span class="penalty">-1 point</span> (weekly)</li>
            <li>Dinner mess left overnight = <span class="penalty">-2 points</span></li>
            <li>2+ days without showering self = <span class="penalty">-3 points</span></li>
            <li>Forgot meds 2+ days = <span class="penalty">-3 points</span></li>
            <li>Didn‚Äôt eat properly 2+ days = <span class="penalty">-3 points</span></li>
